g.title: q1
g.text: Prescription from Endocrinologist or Weight Management Specialist?

g.title: q2
g.text: Patient at least 18 years of age?

g.title: q3
g.text: Baseline BMI 30 kg/m2 or greater with at least one weight-related comorbidity?

g.title: q4
g.text: Patient has attempted to lose weight through KP-approved weight loss program?

g.title: q5
g.text: Patient has documented intolerance or contraindication to all listed medications?

g.title: q6
g.text: Wegovy not used with another weight loss drug or GLP-1 receptor agonist?

g.title: q7
g.text: Initial prescription is limited to a maximum of 30-day supply with 2 refills?

g.title: q8
g.text: For Type 2 DM patients,do they meet both additional criteria?

g.title: q9
g.text: Patient continues to meet initial review criteria?

g.title: q10
g.text: Documented weight loss of at least 10% from baseline weight in the past 3 months?
